<br>
1.  Achieve at least Dubious status in Neriak.  This wold later become a demand that you become an Ally.<br>
2.  Learn both Teir Dal and Dark Speach to excellent.<br>
3.  Obtain the approval of all three members of the Triad.  You must seek out myself, Khasirath and Daiunus and prove to us that your Hatred is sincere.  When these things have happened, we will discuss your petition.<br>
<br>
Hate's path is difficult for all - more difficult still for those not blessed with the Birthright of the Prince of Hate.<br>
<br>
